    "You let the warmth of the signed page radiate into your chest. The VeryPositive warmth floods you — triumph tempered with humility. The VeryHigh arousal that carried you to this moment eases into a vibrant, alive"
    "energy: you will sleep badly tonight; you will wake early; you will argue and build and sometimes fail. But you will not be alone."
    "You walk with Kaito Sakamura under the lamps, the air salt-cooled and honest. In the distance, a child runs ahead to flatten a palm against the promenade tile, leaving a damp print that will weather into"
